history: Uspatih was founded in 2007, precisely on July 11, at the initiation of Nusyirwan DN, Ronny AS, and HnQ Gunawan in providing digital-based printing service space in Padang Panjang which initially rented 1 shophouse plot located at Jl. Soekarno Hatta Bukit Surungan, when Uspatih was first established, it still focused on cutting sticker products and outdoor products by relying on JINKA brand cutting machines and GONZHENG brand outdoor machines, to support production, so in 2010 Uspatih had another ROLAND brand machine which can produce various types of products, such as: Motorcycle Striping, T-shirts, Banners, Photos and other creative products. \nIn 2013 Uspatih was able to have his own shophouse located at Jl. Abu Hanifah No.10 Kampung Jambak, Padang Panjang City which is occupied until now, at the same time Uspatih sold the GONZHENG Outdoor machine and replaced it with the ICONTEC TW33HD series. Uspatih brought in a Roland brand plotter machine which only lasted 6 months because there were no human resources to operate it. In 2015 Uspatih brought in a MIMAKI type TS3-1600 machine which can produce fabric materials with sublime textiles including: Football Jerseys, Trail, futsal, Bicycles, Pillows , Flags and other types of products which until now have been Uspatih's mainstay in serving printing-based textile needs. \nAt the beginning of 2017, Uspatih tried to add a division, namely Website and Application creation services, which to date has created several applications including: SmartEdu Padang Panjang (Education service application), Rumahku.id (Property marketplace application), SmartDishub (Padang Panjang Transportation service application ), Apps Pageone esport,  and others.
